FedEqual: Defending Model Poisoning Attacks in Heterogeneous Federated Learning
Publisher: IEEE
Cite This
PDF
Ling-Yuan Chen ; Te-Chuan Chiu ; Ai-Chun Pang ; Li-Chen Cheng
